# agentic-ai

A progressive Python framework for building agentic AI systems with **Google Gemini**.

Covers everything from simple talking agents to RAG pipelines and MCP tool servers.

---

## Installation

```bash
pip install agentic-ai
```

Set your Gemini API key:

```bash
export GEMINI_API_KEY="your-key-here"
```

---

## Quick start

```python
from agentic_ai.agents.base import BaseAgent

agent = BaseAgent("Alfred", "You are a witty British butler.")
agent.think("Good morning! What should I do today?")
```

---

## Package layout

```
agentic_ai/
├── agents/
│   ├── base.py            # BaseAgent — memory, streaming, facts
│   ├── tool_agent.py      # ToolAgent — Gemini function-calling
│   ├── json_agent.py      # JsonAgent — always returns parsed dict
│   └── reasoning_agent.py # ReasoningAgent — surfaces chain-of-thought
├── memory/
│   ├── short_term.py      # Sliding-window turn memory
│   ├── long_term.py       # SQLite-backed persistent memory
│   └── shared.py          # Thread-safe shared state across agents
├── tools/
│   ├── registry.py        # @tool decorator and ToolRegistry
│   └── builtins.py        # get_weather, add_numbers, search_wikipedia
├── patterns/
│   ├── orchestrator.py    # run_conversation, run_supervisor
│   ├── parallel.py        # run_parallel (fan-out)
│   └── debate.py          # run_debate (two agents + judge)
├── rag/
│   ├── chunker.py         # chunk_text
│   ├── embedder.py        # embed_texts (Gemini text-embedding-004)
│   ├── vector_store.py    # In-memory cosine-similarity store
│   └── rag_agent.py       # RAGAgent (ingest + retrieve + generate)
└── mcp/
    ├── server.py          # MCPServer — HTTP tool server
    └── client.py          # MCPClient — calls a running MCPServer
```

---

## Examples

All examples live in `agentic_ai/examples/` and can be run directly:

| File | Concept |
|------|---------|
| `01_talking_agents.py` | Two agents in a round-robin conversation |
| `02_personality_and_memory.py` | Agent with persona + short-term memory |
| `03_tool_agent_weather.py` | Real weather tool via Gemini function-calling |
| `04_json_agent.py` | Guaranteed structured JSON output |
| `05_reasoning_agent.py` | Chain-of-thought planner → executor pipeline |
| `06_supervisor.py` | Supervisor delegates to specialist workers |
| `07_parallel_agents.py` | Fan-out: same task, multiple agents in parallel |
| `08_debate.py` | Two agents debate; a judge picks a winner |
| `09_long_term_memory.py` | SQLite-backed memory across sessions |
| `10_rag_agent.py` | Document ingestion + retrieval-augmented generation |
| `11_mcp_demo.py` | MCP tool server + agent integration |

